{"tid":961712,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］ 陳 曉 東 驚 變 塑 膠 人","createTime":"2018-12-30T10:32:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T15:49:29.000Z","uid":215823,"like":9,"dislike":199,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"dbf5155848e07f923b4d8b11c0c2fad6b342125d","tid":961712,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T10:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/30/183119_40b88a443c0e967940c5386761f2c01c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F30%2F183119_40b88a443c0e967940c5386761f2c01c.png&h=abdb3d7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/30/183125_83ba71d9a48da20c5fd61628b8c7bdac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F30%2F183125_83ba71d9a48da20c5fd61628b8c7bdac.png&h=cddab2c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/30/183130_ee9098a35d1fc0bd0331768295175eb1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F30%2F183130_ee9098a35d1fc0bd0331768295175eb1.png&h=602e28fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現年42歲的歌手陳曉東（東東）一向保養得宜，暫別香港樂壇多年樣貌依舊，早前返港出席萬希泉活動及接受東網專訪。對於多年來被指整容，他完全不介意，更突然出手捽面，在左邊臉用手指用力捽左捽右，捽足4秒，面珠更瞬間留下手指印，他說：「啲人話我塑膠造，是但啦，因為呢個世界keep得好，就話你玻尿酸，keep得唔好，就話你老成咁，你想我點，拉爛塊面咩！郁得㗎！唔係唔郁得！作為藝人，每一個階段自然有每一個階段嘅樣，我只會愈嚟愈老，有一日好快皺紋會出晒嚟，係另一樣嘢，好彩我本身屬baby fat，我好鍾意清潔，有潔癖，我鍾意抹面乾淨，會用護膚品，都貪靚。」"},{"pid":"ab124251432a97b3dcffa3a4062ce6b90e9266b7","tid":961712,"uid":215823,"like":422,"dislike":1,"score":421,"quote":{"pid":"dbf5155848e07f923b4d8b11c0c2fad6b342125d","tid":961712,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T10:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/30/183119_40b88a443c0e967940c5386761f2c01c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F30%2F183119_40b88a443c0e967940c5386761f2c01c.png&h=abdb3d7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/30/183125_83ba71d9a48da20c5fd61628b8c7bdac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F30%2F183125_83ba71d9a48da20c5fd61628b8c7bdac.png&h=cddab2c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/30/183130_ee9098a35d1fc0bd0331768295175eb1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F30%2F183130_ee9098a35d1fc0bd0331768295175eb1.png&h=602e28fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現年42歲的歌手陳曉東（東東）一向保養得宜，暫別香港樂壇多年樣貌依舊，早前返港出席萬希泉活動及接受東網專訪。對於多年來被指整容，他完全不介意，更突然出手捽面，在左邊臉用手指用力捽左捽右，捽足4秒，面珠更瞬間留下手指印，他說：「啲人話我塑膠造，是但啦，因為呢個世界keep得好，就話你玻尿酸，keep得唔好，就話你老成咁，你想我點，拉爛塊面咩！郁得㗎！唔係唔郁得！作為藝人，每一個階段自然有每一個階段嘅樣，我只會愈嚟愈老，有一日好快皺紋會出晒嚟，係另一樣嘢，好彩我本身屬baby fat，我好鍾意清潔，有潔癖，我鍾意抹面乾淨，會用護膚品，都貪靚。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T10:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/30/183425_b31a1c145a232ec12af676c7ae5a6738.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F30%2F183425_b31a1c145a232ec12af676c7ae5a6738.png&h=39ff2428&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c70538ad15a5ae6f0f87ba3825e75368d756b8eb","tid":961712,"uid":9683,"like":307,"dislike":3,"score":304,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T10:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://missmokmok.files.wordpress.com/2014/12/woody.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmissmokmok.files.wordpress.com%2F2014%2F12%2Fwoody.jpg&h=999f7500&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f770b3edd8309f33d0dfe4cfdd36b14bcb0d5820","tid":961712,"uid":126841,"like":82,"dislike":4,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T10:37:42.000Z","msg":"男人老狗整到對眉成個女人咁"},{"pid":"97fd23ffa2709294587985381113b4b8d68f6679","tid":961712,"uid":107364,"like":4,"dislike":54,"score":-50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T10:3